      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage, so it's as pristine as they come. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
