    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This S54-powered icon represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated precision. The engine benefits from a documented rod bearing service and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory-spec urgency. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers for optimized turn-in and lateral stability. Finished in immaculate Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains its deep luster with no evidence of panel gap variance or paint degradation. A turn-key specimen for the collector who demands mechanical integrity and a pure, linear power band.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
