    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirls, scratches, or stone chips, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and a strict hand-wash-only regimen. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the factory alloy wheels are entirely free of curb rash, wrapped in premium performance tires with nearly full tread depth. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition; the leather upholstery shows no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets have been protected by original floor mats, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at authorized service centers with a full paper trail of preventative maintenance. It comes complete with both original keys, the owner's manual, and a clean history. This vehicle drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car, offering a flawless experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
